{#
  The bridge gateway is this host's own traffic: netavark's hairpin DNAT
  masquerades host-local and container queries to a published port into
  10.88.0.1, so the host plus every container resolving through aardvark
  collapse into one client. Label it honestly instead of showing
  host.containers.internal.
#}
